{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3d78a96213","title":"党委应以顾问身份保留在学校","origin":"《云南省高等学校右派分子反动言论选集》(中国共产党云南省高等学校委员会办公室编印，1957.8.15)，内部资料 注意保存。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8d89b0a4bd","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":28,"articleId":"3d78a96213"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"722102ffad","name":"昆明工学院学生"},{"id":"c53616b105","name":"王维中"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"ba034c3f49","type":"title","text":"党委应以顾问身份保留在学校","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"ff34c5665a","type":"authors","text":"昆明工学院学生王维中","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"5edcfe05e7","type":"subtitle","text":"(王维中：昆明工学院机械系学生)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"52d950203c","type":"appellation","text":"编辑同志：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"90d6f6d5a7","type":"paragraph","text":"吾阅22期院刊，其上有胡大敏同学的七个基本论点，吾同意其一部分，并另有一点补充。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"974ea12d86","type":"paragraph","text":"一、关于我国目前人事制度不合理问题，吾有同感。凡事总以事实为主，就以我院为例，院长是办学校的外行，以他为首的“兵”的系统把持着我院的行政机构；而真有办法才干的人，都当教授了。上述情况对军管时期来说，到是必不可少的一种制度。因初解放，社会秩序不安定，的确要一些军人代政，否则就会出乱子，而现在情况变了，建设时期应让有经验的能治校的人治校，党委则可以顾问身份保留在学校，并不否定党的领导。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"a1b1dcc25c","type":"paragraph","text":"二、关于高饶事件：必须从太平天国得到教训，高饶虽是野心家（？） 也不应该一棒打死。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"a437c8b929","type":"paragraph","text":"三、对于右派分子不应有人身攻击，辱人人格，特别是民主党派人士，倘然他们经整风后态度有所改变，对自己的言论彻底批判，那末现在的攻击影响不是很不好吗？况大放大鸣，反正他们跑不了，应以理服之，以后的关系才好处，不要事先挖根底翻祖宗……党中央和毛主席真英明，不动刀兵，反革命自投罗网，真可谓古今中外肃反之创举。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"bfda5e537e","type":"paragraph","text":"四、最后党团群分校问题，本人不同意这样办。我认为社会上及青年学生都可不要党团组织，大家不分彼此，毫无思想意识上的隔膜，也不会产生三大主义。有人会问，那末，不要党了这不是右派分子是谁？不，我说党团员可以作为一行职业，他们专管政治，作一辈子的职业党团员，由中央分派到各机关、军队、学校、工厂……宣传党团的思想政策，照章办事。有了脱产职业党团员，办事就好多了，由于分工严密，没有跨职现象，三个主义不反自灭，社会自然安定。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"5fca9068cb","type":"paragraph","text":"这是本人一点粗浅的看法，倘有不对，希望诸君以理服之，切莫施以人身攻击，况本人最懂道理，果然理亏，自当低头于真理，决不狡辩，诸君果能如此，本人万幸！","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"7b9fac499a","type":"paragraph","text":"左中右 于57.6.28(注：此信是写给昆明工学院院刊的，标题是编者所加)","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"5e7d6ac0ca","type":"subtitle","text":"王维中(昆明工学院机械系学生)大字报：","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"331e4bada5","type":"subtitle","text":"虹山上","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"b3287d6de1","type":"paragraph","text":"迷糊睡梦中，置身虹山上，","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"7acc9acae4","type":"paragraph","text":"举目望，交岔路口小瓦房，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"889f5c5260","type":"paragraph","text":"愁风惨，灯昏黄，","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"4cb22a6599","type":"paragraph","text":"白色鬼影乱飘摇，","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"749a4162fa","type":"paragraph","text":"手执朱笔把魂勾，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"0748d5fabb","type":"paragraph","text":"有的快抓来，有的慢慢搞；","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"54d3b63964","type":"paragraph","text":"有的到鬼门关挂了预约号，","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"50b40b47ab","type":"paragraph","text":"有的甚至把命丧。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"ed2c46ce4b","type":"paragraph","text":"巴山夜雨听不见，","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"11ae42b522","type":"paragraph","text":"惟有虹山风怒嚎。","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"3ef0bfa979","type":"paragraph","text":"………………","index":23,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"5e5b0cf2e4","type":"paragraph","text":"（注：原无题，现题为编者所加。工学院地址即在虹山）","index":24,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"a573c5375e","type":"subtitle","text":"道琴申冤","index":25,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"c952a236a5","type":"paragraph","text":"工学院里一堂神，","index":26,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"4fbff75c51","type":"paragraph","text":"神五神六生是非，","index":27,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"d903c79496","type":"paragraph","text":"穷苦工人遭邪气，","index":28,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"5201293cd3","type":"paragraph","text":"小小职员难安生，","index":29,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"fc1062a279","type":"paragraph","text":"需献浆水饭一碗，","index":30,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"e93c327f60","type":"paragraph","text":"又因员工不信神，","index":31,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"2d4e0852b6","type":"paragraph","text":"一回不献成笔帐，","index":32,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"2b704e144f","type":"paragraph","text":"几次不献脑怒神，","index":33,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"da827b1e7e","type":"paragraph","text":"有遭（朝）一日运动到，","index":34,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"9c0d680481","type":"paragraph","text":"诸神齐全了不成，","index":35,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"30f394df01","type":"paragraph","text":"左手提着王圣旨，","index":36,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"f4ac27e2ca","type":"paragraph","text":"右手拿着捆仙绳，","index":37,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"6dd5992836","type":"paragraph","text":"直言之人偕前跪，","index":38,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"ee1bf03d25","type":"paragraph","text":"整的尽是老实人，","index":39,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"c0b693c4cf","type":"paragraph","text":"东狱庙里不烧纸，","index":40,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"d5d089bf44","type":"paragraph","text":"城隍会上得罪神，","index":41,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"5994930761","type":"paragraph","text":"收刷一场灾临下，","index":42,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"41fb37cfbe","type":"paragraph","text":"生死簿上有你名，","index":43,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"f38bd686fd","type":"paragraph","text":"一个一个提来整，","index":44,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"eff855f8d4","type":"paragraph","text":"整死一百伍十双，","index":45,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"e65fb533a8","type":"paragraph","text":"若问诸神名何姓，","index":46,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"098eced04d","type":"paragraph","text":"听我山人诉一番，","index":47,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"9f749f484e","type":"paragraph","text":"秘书科里有一个，","index":48,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"fadc55e96f","type":"paragraph","text":"…………………","index":49,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"a0444e50d4","type":"paragraph","text":"…………………","index":50,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"6704c5af85","type":"paragraph","text":"（以下是对党员干部逐人进行攻击，从略）","index":51,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"9a0bcca2eb","type":"paragraph","text":"一堂神这么几个，","index":52,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"3216b2d6b2","type":"paragraph","text":"害死多少命苦人，","index":53,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"362be0fe3c","type":"paragraph","text":"请诸公休息一会","index":54,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"},{"id":"7c168e610e","type":"paragraph","text":"唱二段更加好听。（未署名）","index":55,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213"}],"page":{"id":"46127031f4","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"3d78a96213","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}